---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Granny Flats Frankston & Mornington Peninsula | Full Service Area | (03) 9003 0108"
  description="Granny flat &amp; second dwelling builders across the full Frankston City and Mornington Peninsula Shire. 25+ suburbs covered. VicSmart fast-track, full planning permit, NDIS SDA. Free consultation."
  canonical="https://frankstongrannyflats.com.au/mornington-peninsula/">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Frankston City &middot; Mornington Peninsula Shire</span>
      <h1>Granny flats across <span class="accent">Frankston &amp; the Mornington Peninsula</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        From Seaford in the north to Portsea in the south, Mt Eliza on the bay to
        Hastings on Western Port &mdash; we cover both Frankston City and Mornington
        Peninsula Shire municipalities. Council permit lodgement included on every
        quote.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book a free consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Full coverage</span>
      <h2>Suburbs we cover.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Featured suburb pages.</h3>
        <p>We&rsquo;ve written full local guides for each of these &mdash; council jurisdiction, block-size typical, what we usually spec, what jobs typically cost.</p>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <a class="area-pill" href="/frankston-south/">Frankston South</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/mt-eliza/">Mt Eliza</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/mornington/">Mornington</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/carrum-downs/">Carrum Downs</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/seaford/">Seaford</a>
        </div>

        <h3>Frankston City Council suburbs.</h3>
        <p>Frankston City municipality &mdash; second dwelling allowed on lots &ge;300m&sup2;, VicSmart fast-track for builds &lt;60m&sup2;.</p>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Frankston (CBD)</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Frankston North</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Langwarrin</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Langwarrin South</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Karingal</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Skye</a>
        </div>

        <h3>Mornington Peninsula Shire suburbs.</h3>
        <p>Peninsula Shire municipality &mdash; tighter DDO, HO, ESO, BMO controls. Short-stay registration applies. Different planning scheme to Frankston City.</p>
        <div class="areas-grid" style="margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;">
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Mt Martha</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Mornington Park</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Baxter</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Somerville</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Tyabb</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Moorooduc</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Tuerong</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Hastings</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Crib Point</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Bittern</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Balnarring</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Merricks Beach</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Shoreham</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Red Hill</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Main Ridge</a>
          <a class="area-pill" href="/quote/">Flinders</a>
        </div>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Two councils, two pathways.</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Frankston City Council</strong> &mdash; permit fees around $1,500&ndash;$3,000
          for VicSmart, $4,000&ndash;$8,000 for full planning permit. Decision time
          10 business days (VicSmart) or 60&ndash;90 days (full). Pre-application
          meeting recommended for jobs &gt;60m&sup2;.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Mornington Peninsula Shire</strong> &mdash; permit fees similar but
          additional overlay-specific conditions (DDO design controls, HO heritage
          impact statement, BMO bushfire management plan, ESO environmental
          significance). Pre-application meeting often mandatory in HO precincts.
          Decision time 90&ndash;120 days for overlay-affected sites.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">All five formats</span>
      <h2>What we build.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/one-bedroom/">
          <h3>1-Bedroom</h3>
          <p>35&ndash;50m&sup2;. $90K&ndash;$180K. Ageing parent or adult child.</p>
          <span class="svc-link">See 1-bedroom &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/two-bedroom/">
          <h3>2-Bedroom</h3>
          <p>60&ndash;90m&sup2;. $140K&ndash;$220K. Couples or rental.</p>
          <span class="svc-link">See 2-bedroom &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/dual-occupancy/">
          <h3>Dual-Occupancy</h3>
          <p>90&ndash;130m&sup2;. $180K&ndash;$280K. Subdivision-ready.</p>
          <span class="svc-link">See dual-occupancy &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/garden-studios/">
          <h3>Garden Studios</h3>
          <p>12&ndash;25m&sup2;. $25K&ndash;$95K. No permit needed.</p>
          <span class="svc-link">See studios &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/ndis-sda/">
          <h3>NDIS SDA</h3>
          <p>$300K&ndash;$600K. SDA provider rental income.</p>
          <span class="svc-link">See NDIS SDA &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free consultation across Frankston &amp; Peninsula.</h2>
        <p>Tell us your address and we&rsquo;ll come out, measure, check the zone, give you the honest answer in 60 min.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
